{"tid":127104,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]希望發動連登力量幫我搵返好緊要既卡片套","createTime":"2017-02-20T00:19:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-24T09:53:14.000Z","uid":14256,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fde08847326ea7d494b49214d0d66bd229d6f7f4","tid":127104,"uid":14256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T00:19:39.000Z","msg":"今次真係要連登眾巴絲幫幫忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今朝6點半果時搭的士去健威花園 途中跌左個啡色卡片套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入面d卡其實一D都唔重要...但係個卡片套係女朋友五週年紀念果時自己手造送俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後面有個五既mark架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我記得架的士係J字頭 新型4座既 前座頸枕位有條鐵通<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望有巴絲見到可以俾我知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相得一張仲要淨係得背面<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望你地會認到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/20/081917_97e744e63e4fd345755043f937d0c1a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F20%2F081917_97e744e63e4fd345755043f937d0c1a8.jpg&h=70a4227b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces